        <item>
            <title>2.3.1</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 10:00:18 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>48</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.3.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed sidebar sessions instantly closing and bouncing back to the launcher after upgrading to Claude Code extension 2.1.139+. The bundled `vscode` shim now exposes the `tabGroups.onDidChangeTabs` / `onDidChangeTabGroups` events that the extension subscribes to during activation.
]]></description>
